|accessdate=July 14, 2010}}</ref>

The only son of former [[Governor of Oregon|Oregon Governor]] [[Elmo Smith]] and his wife Dorothy,<ref name="rg"/> he is also a cousin of [[Steven Symms]], a former congressman and Senator from [[Idaho]].<ref name="congbio"/>

